name: PEPE
description: This artwork was inspired by a Tiktok challenge popularized by Mimiyuuuh, a local influencer and celebrity, where she's seen grooving to an old song called "Kabet" by Gagong Rapper while doing her "pabebe" moves. I had this funny visual in my head of Jose "Pepe" Rizal, our national hero, acting like a pabebe upon seeing Josephine Bracken for the very first time.
